Informed Consent: This research project is being conducted by Dr. Georgia Mavrommati from School for the Environment at University of Massachusetts, Boston, Massachusetts, USA. The purpose of this study is to better understand students’ perceptions of bottled water versus tap water. Your responses are anonymous. Your participation is voluntary. Completion of the survey should take approximately 5-10 minutes. You may choose not to answer any or all questions. Questions about this project may be directed to: and/or Georgia Mavrommati, email: georgia.mavrommati@umb.edu
